originalText.text:
Victoria is one of the most knowledgeable and talented injectors I’ve met. She is beyond personable, patient during the consultation, and does not inject for business but rather enhancing your natural features! She made me extremely comfortable during my treatment session and was walking me through what she was doing step by step.

The rest of the staff was just as amazing, making sure my visit was a pleasant experience and I was leaving happy with my services. Can’t wait to continue services with Prime Medispa!

originalText.text: The entire experience at Prime Medispa was extraordinary! The space is absolutely beautiful and the process of booking services is painless. The front office staff  was very welcoming, knowledgeable and friendly. They walked me through each step of the treatment and listened to all of my concerns to assure that I was comfortable. I highly recommended Prime if you are looking to be relaxed in a clean and modern environment with highly skilled professionals.

originalText.text: I love love love this gorgeous spa! From the moment you walk in you are greeted by a very welcoming staff, everyone is so friendly and so professional. Every corner and every room is meticulously designed, so clean and you truly feel very pampered. Victoria is super professional, so easy to talk to and explained several facial procedures in detail. I realized how little attention I paid to my skin and it has truly been a learning journey and I am beyond grateful! May who is at the front desk even brought a cappuccino and cookies and you just feel very welcomed and genuinely taken care of. Thank you for all you do and for being a very trusting source in my skincare journey!

originalText.text: I had the absolute best experience at Prime Medispa! I did a lymphatic drainage combined with wood therapy and got my very first hydra facial. Both treatments gave me instant results and I walked out of the spa super satisfied and will definitely be back very soon.
